OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA damp end
OL,6,Fto the day with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fcontinuing to clear eastwards. Turning
OL,8,Fdrier overnight with a mixture of
OL,9,Fclear spells and isolated showers.
OL,10,FMilder than last night and staying
OL,11,Ffrost-free.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,14,Fisolated showers until mid to late
OL,15,Fafternoon, then the showers become
OL,16,Fmore widespread, frequent and often
OL,17,Fheavy, with a chance of thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
