OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA
OL,6,Fchilly start to Monday with sunshine
OL,7,Fand showers. Becoming wet and windy
OL,8,Fovernight with rain followed by
OL,9,Fshowers on Tuesday and Wednesday.
OL,10,FTemperatures gradually on the rise.
